uy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B9ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-PIfezt5_wqv2ApvAr3PoMQ">Tương phùng hành - 相逢行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ikky%C5%AB-S%C5%8Djun/V%C4%83n-Minh-lo%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BA%ADu/poem-Fu4A_kkw9Ocq7LIjRuYhdg">Văn Minh loạn hậu - 文明亂後</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ikky%C5%AB-S%C5%8Djun/author-6Fl1CJXNHm-NMj9JU9BqDg">Ikkyū Sōjun</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Y%E1%BB%83u-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u/Xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-nZy9teao4ueIVmpfTQIMLQ">Xuân tứ kỳ 1 - 春思其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Y%E1%BB%83u-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87u/author-2QZmBHuhdS8jfIiDaowtCg">Trương Yểu Điệu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
